    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Education Performance Analysis'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='800' maxwidth='1200' minheight='800' minwidth='1200' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='19000' id='12' type-v2='dashboard-object' w='98666' x='667' y='68000'>
            <button action='tabdoc:goto-sheet window-id=&quot;{E9049069-A1DB-4433-84F3-375CA8BD00A9}&quot;' button-type='text'>
              <button-visual-state>
                <caption>District Deep Dive</caption>
                <button-caption-font-style bold='true' fontcolor='#ffffff' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='16' />
                <format attr='background-color' value='#1295d8' />
              </button-visual-state>
            </button>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='19000' id='5' type-v2='text' w='98666' x='667' y='1000'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#222222' fontname='Arial' fontsize='28'>District Performance Relative to Socioeconomic Expectations</run>
              <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Arial' fontsize='13'>This analysis evaluates whether districts outperform or underperform predicted math achievements based on socioeconomic conditions</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='30250' id='6' type-v2='text' w='98666' x='667' y='20000'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#222222' fontname='Arial' fontsize='14'>Significant Findings:</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Socioeconomic status (SES) strongly predicts math performance... but not perfectly</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>          - There is a clear positive relationship between SES index and math proficiency however, the residual math score shows meaningful variation around that prediction</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Some lower SES districts consistently outperform expectations</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>          - High performance is not exclusively tied to advantages</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Over the three years I analyzed, there were some districts imprving relative to predictions, others declining and some who were stable</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>          - District performance relative to expectations is dynamic, not fixed, showing that interventions and/or strategies may matter</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='12000' id='17' type-v2='text' w='98666' x='667' y='87000'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#222222' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Created by Zachary Niccoli</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#222222' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Data Modeling in Python, SQL and Tableau</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#222222' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Data Source: California Department of Education (ed-data.org)</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#222222' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Years Analyzed: 2021–2023</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#222222' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Modeling: Linear regression modeling of SES vs math achievement</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone fixed-size='135' h='17750' id='11' is-fixed='true' type-v2='dashboard-object' w='98666' x='667' y='50250'>
            <button action='tabdoc:goto-sheet window-id=&quot;{A8B31FE4-1D66-4710-AB45-13EE51F81B1E}&quot;' button-type='text'>
              <button-visual-state>
                <caption>Which Districts are Beating Socioeconomic Expectations?</caption>
                <button-caption-font-style bold='true' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='16' />
                <format attr='background-color' value='#ffb511' />
              </button-visual-state>
            </button>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <devicelayouts>
        <devicelayout auto-generated='true' name='Phone'>
          <size maxheight='700' minheight='700' sizing-mode='vscroll' />
          <zones>
            <zone h='100000' id='31' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
              <zone h='98000' id='30' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98666' x='667' y='1000'>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='19000' id='5' type-v2='text' w='98666' x='667' y='1000'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#222222' fontname='Arial' fontsize='28'>District Performance Relative to Socioeconomic Expectations</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Arial' fontsize='13'>This analysis evaluates whether districts outperform or underperform predicted math achievements based on socioeconomic conditions</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone forceUpdate='true' h='30250' id='6' type-v2='text' w='98666' x='667' y='20000'>
                  <formatted-text>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#222222' fontname='Arial' fontsize='14'>Significant Findings:</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Socioeconomic status (SES) strongly predicts math performance... but not perfectly</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>          - There is a clear positive relationship between SES index and math proficiency however, the residual math score shows meaningful variation around that prediction</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Some lower SES districts consistently outperform expectations</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>          - High performance is not exclusively tied to advantages</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>- Over the three years I analyzed, there were some districts imprving relative to predictions, others declining and some who were stable</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#4b4b4b' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>          - District performance relative to expectations is dynamic, not fixed, showing that interventions and/or strategies may matter</run>
                  </formatted-text>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone fixed-size='135' h='17750' id='11' type-v2='dashboard-object' w='98666' x='667' y='50250'>
                  <button action='tabdoc:goto-sheet window-id=&quot;{A8B31FE4-1D66-4710-AB45-13EE51F81B1E}&quot;' button-type='text'>
                    <button-visual-state>
                      <caption>Which Districts are Beating Socioeconomic Expectations?</caption>
                      <button-caption-font-style bold='true' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='16' />
                      <format attr='background-color' value='#ffb511' />
                    </button-visual-state>
                  </button>
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='padding' value='0' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone h='19000' id='12' type-v2='dashboard-object' w='98666' x='667' y='68000'>
                  <button action='tabdoc:goto-sheet window-id=&quot;{E9049069-A1DB-4433-84F3-375CA8BD00A9}&quot;' button-type='text'>
